Version 0.2a
------------

We are pleased to announce the release of version 0.2a of myHadoop, which
enables the use of Apache Hadoop in a non-dedicated cluster environment,
being administered by typical batch scheduler. 

This release adds to the 0.1 release as follows:
* Support for the Sun Grid Engine (SGE)
* Updated documentation for SGE and PBS

Please feel free to send questions/comments/concerns to the myHadoop
mailing list at myhadoop-users@lists.sourceforge.net. You may also send
individual private comments to Sriram Krishnan at sriram@sdsc.edu.

Sincerely,
Sriram
